OL,13,Fbackbenches before being appointed as
OL,14,Fa junior environment minister by Ms
OL,15,FSturgeon.
OL,17,FBy 2023, she has been promoted to net
OL,18,Fzero secretary by then first minister
OL,19,FHumza Yousaf.
